# Task 1: Digital Literacy Awareness Infographic

For this task, I created a digital literacy awareness infographic using Canva. The aim of the design is to educate students about the importance of digital literacy in everyday academic and professional life.

The infographic covers key topics such as the definition of digital literacy, useful digital tools for students, internet safety practices, professional online presence, and email etiquette. These elements were selected to provide a complete overview of how students can effectively and responsibly use digital platforms.

While designing the infographic, I focused on maintaining clarity, visual balance, and easy readability so that the information can be quickly understood. One interesting aspect was organizing multiple concepts into a single page without making it cluttered.

This task helped me understand the importance of presenting digital knowledge in a visually engaging and structured format.
